Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.59,0:00:06.22,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}There's something fascinating about stars,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.22,0:00:08.10,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}be they criminals or actors.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.10,0:00:09.77,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Today's stage is a village shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.77,0:00:12.90,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Another meaning to the letters we've been seeing hides an unexpected secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.90,0:00:14.43,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.43,0:00:16.17,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.17,0:00:18.20,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.70,0:02:00.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rhinoceros beetles, rhinoceros beetles!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.39,0:02:03.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fun to catch beetles!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.86,0:02:05.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.22,0:02:10.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gotta be around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.59,0:02:20.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to look for bugs
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.24,0:02:24.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,on a hot day like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.78,0:02:29.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mitsuhiko. Are you sure they're around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.09,0:02:33.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait {\i1}just{\i0} a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.42,0:02:39.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And there's trash everywhere! Way up on this mountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.66,0:02:42.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.25,0:02:45.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The villagers usually keep this forest tidy,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.66,0:02:50.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but the place was swarming with revelers last night, thanks to the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.67,0:02:53.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,F-Festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.57,0:02:55.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's called the Tentō Festival, or Festival of Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.65,0:03:00.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Giant carts carrying images of the Shinto gods are pulled through town!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.63,0:03:02.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See that shrine over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.61,0:03:06.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's where the festival carts begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:11.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They shoot fireworks behind the gods!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.24,0:03:13.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What a magnificent sight it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.22,0:03:17.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.35,0:03:20.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, er...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.52,0:03:26.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you invite us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.57,0:03:28.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.40,0:03:30.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna see fireworks too!
